QuestData.Title: The Hayward Brothers
QuestData.Description: The Hayward Fishery can be found far to the south. The Hayward brothers have been running it for years.$B$BThey don't make it to town very often, except to trade their fish. Send word to them that the evacuation is underway.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Sebastian Hayward at the Hayward Fishery.
QuestData.RewardText: You here to give us a hand?
